reviews.review_text: End of a great summer Was at this show when I was 16. Hitched from Colorado,ended up in boulder after the shows a few weeks before. Got the last ride to Long Beach with some Christian kids coming home from bible camp with a QP of Colombian In the car. Went to the Vegas show. Got a ride back to the east coast in the back of a pickup. Never did make it back to Herricks high school again. Not after that summer. Elevator mechanics don’t need a HS diploma. 57 now and still listening to the dead daily.
